Package: lolspotr
Type: Package
Title: League of Legends Statistic Calculators
Version: 0.1
Date: 2022-05-01
Author: Albert Brigino <abrigino@usf.edu>
Maintainer: <abrigino@usf.edu>
Description: Simplifies League of Legends statistic calculations
    into separate, easily-accessible functions (as described by Riot Games).
    Takes inputs regarding stats provided from in-game abilities,
    masteries and items and returns calculated statistic.
Depends: R (>= 4.0) 
Imports: 
    rvest,
    magrittr
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
